"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US has announced that it will allow ships to pass through the Strait of Hormuz, provided they are not heading to or from Iranian ports. On Tuesday, tracking data showed at least two tankers making the passage.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Allows Ships Through Strait\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estados Unidos ha dicho que dejar\u00e1 pasar barcos por el Estrecho de Hormuz, si no van o vienen de puertos iran\u00edes. El martes, datos mostraron al menos dos barcos pasando.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EEUU deja pasar barcos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Lebanon, the government is entering peace talks, but it has limited influence over the involved group. Meanwhile, in Pakistan, there are reports of hospital staff injecting patients without gloves and reusing syringes, though the hospital's management denies these claims.\",            \"english_title\": \"Lebanon Peace Talks and Pakistan Hospital Issues\",            \"translated_version\": \"En L\u00edbano, el gobierno est\u00e1 en conversaciones de paz, pero tiene poca influencia sobre el grupo involucrado. Mientras tanto, en Pakist\u00e1n, hay reportes de personal de hospital inyectando pacientes sin guantes y reutilizando jeringas, aunque la administraci\u00f3n del hospital niega esto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones de paz en L\u00edbano y problemas en hospital de Pakist\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Nabatieh, a city that was once lively but is now deserted, BBC Middle East correspondent Hugo Bachega is accompanying paramedics on duty to report on the situation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nabatieh's Current Situation\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Nabatieh, una ciudad que antes era animada pero ahora est\u00e1 vac\u00eda, el corresponsal de BBC Medio Oriente Hugo Bachega acompa\u00f1a a param\u00e9dicos para informar sobre la situaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Situaci\u00f3n en Nabatieh\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia has proposed 'pragmatic' relations, but P\u00e9ter Magyar has stated he will not personally contact Vladimir Putin.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russia's Proposal for Relations\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia ha propuesto relaciones `pragm\u00e1ticas`, pero P\u00e9ter Magyar ha dicho que no contactar\u00e1 personalmente a Vladimir Putin.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Propuesta de Rusia para relaciones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Four women have accused a congressman and former candidate for California governor of misconduct, including sexual harassment and rape, which he has denied.\",            \"english_title\": \"Accusations Against Congressman\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cuatro mujeres han acusado a un congresista y ex candidato a gobernador de California de mala conducta, incluyendo acoso sexual y violaci\u00f3n, lo cual \u00e9l ha negado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acusaciones contra congresista\"        }    ]}"